resources.string:
* Search Youtube --> How to Bypass FRP for [device name] [model]
* Follow Instructions to open chrome
* Download this instead of *any* Shortcut app
* Open this apk from downloads
* Enable "Unknown Sources"
* Install This App, then Open
* Open Developer Options
* Click on OEM Unlock and hold 2 sec
* Enable OEM Unlock
* Go to Settings
* Factory Reset
* Done
